# ── Live football scores (optional) ─────────────────────────────────────────
# OnlyFootballsFan shows real live scores when this is set; otherwise it falls
# back to demo fixtures so the site always works.
#
# 1. Get a FREE token (covers the World Cup + major leagues):
#    https://www.football-data.org/client/register
# 2. Copy this file to ".env.local" and paste your token below.
# 3. Restart the dev/prod server.
#
# NOTE: keep your real token in .env.local (gitignored), NOT here — this file
# is committed to git, so it must never contain a real key.
FOOTBALL_DATA_TOKEN=
